---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Resume — Shelly Xiong"
  description="Experience and skills — Shelly Xiong, software developer, designer, and birder based in New York City."
>
  <main style="padding-top: calc(var(--nav-height) + 40px);">
    <section class="section experience" id="experience">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Experience</h2>
        <div class="timeline">
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <h3>Website Administrator</h3>
              <p class="timeline-org">The Metropolitan Museum of Art</p>
              <p class="timeline-location">New York, NY</p>
              <p>Managing the design, development, and maintenance of the Met's e-commerce and transactional web platforms built on Umbraco CMS and .NET. Developing with C#/Razor, HTML/CSS, and JavaScript. Enhancing the ticket purchase experience, implementing performance metrics and tracking, conducting user testing, and ensuring WCAG accessibility compliance.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <h3>Senior Software Developer</h3>
              <p class="timeline-org">Nelson-Atkins Museum of Art</p>
              <p class="timeline-location">Kansas City, MO</p>
              <p>Built and maintained the museum's web properties and digital infrastructure on WordPress. Integrated disparate systems including CMS, ticketing via Tessitura/TNEW, collections via eMuseum, and the online store. Implemented IIIF for digital collections. Published content and ensured mobile-responsive, cross-platform functionality.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <h3>IT Specialist &amp; Web Developer</h3>
              <p class="timeline-org">Marine Corps Community Services</p>
              <p class="timeline-location">Okinawa, Japan</p>
              <p>Maintained and developed web content for MCCS Okinawa on Joomla and SharePoint, supporting digital services for Marines and their families. Managed event calendars and registration systems, built responsive pages with Bootstrap, and provided technical support for installation web services.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <h3>Visual Information Specialist &amp; Web Designer</h3>
              <p class="timeline-org">U.S. Air Force</p>
              <p class="timeline-location">Okinawa, Japan</p>
              <p>Provided marketing and design support for the 18th Force Support Squadron at Kadena Air Base. Created brochures, flyers, posters, signage, and branding materials. Designed and maintained the FSS website, conducted content audits, and coordinated web updates to promote squadron programs, events, and community services.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <h3>Maker Education Educator</h3>
              <p class="timeline-org">Omaha Children's Museum</p>
              <p class="timeline-location">Omaha, NE</p>
              <p>Facilitated hands-on making and tinkering activities in the museum's Tinker Factory makerspace. Designed and led STEAM programming, teaching children and families to use tools including sewing machines, hand tools, and power tools. Created curriculum introducing engineering, science, and art concepts through open-ended making.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section skills" id="skills">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Skills</h2>
        <div class="skills-grid">
          <div class="skill-group">
            <h3>Development</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>HTML5 / CSS3 / JavaScript</li>
              <li>C# / .NET</li>
              <li>Astro / Cloudflare Pages + Workers</li>
              <li>Canvas API</li>
              <li>REST APIs (eBird, Met Open Access)</li>
              <li>WordPress / Joomla</li>
              <li>Web accessibility (WCAG)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="skill-group">
            <h3>Design</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Graphic &amp; web design</li>
              <li>UI / UX design</li>
              <li>Illustration</li>
              <li>Typography</li>
              <li>Colour theory</li>
              <li>Print design</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="skill-group">
            <h3>Making</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Mokuhanga (woodblock)</li>
              <li>Pottery &amp; kintsugi</li>
              <li>Risograph</li>
              <li>Zine making</li>
              <li>3D printing</li>
              <li>Laser cutting</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
